Name: Veg kabab
Desc: cooked mixed vegetable mixture is shaped around the skewers and grill to the perfection.

Name: Bread Roll
Desc: the bread is stuffed with spiced potato-peas mixture and shaped into roll. These stuffed bread roll are fried till crisp and golden brown.

Name: Samosa
Desc: A samosa is a fried pastry with savoury filling of potatoes,onions and peas.It is served with one or two different dippings.

Name: Paneer Manchurian Dry
Desc: Deep fried, crispy paneer cubes are coated with spicy, sour and slightly sweet Indo-chinese sauce. Best served as a starter or snack.

Name: Veg manchurian dry
Desc: This is the Indo Chinese starter dish where fried vegetable balls are coated with thick, flavorful sauce. Since this is the dry version there is no gravy.

Name: Shami Kebab
Desc: Shami Kebab are smoked minced spicy meat appetizers which can be served for your house parties as appetisers. Do try it and we are sure you will love it.

Name: Cheesy Chicken Tikka
Desc: Cheesy Chicken Tikka Recipe is a delicious and indulgent party appetizer with double marinated chicken tikka with lovely melt in the mouth cheese. Serve it along with Dahi Pudina Chutney and some pickled onions.

Name: Crispy Chicken Popcorn
Desc: Chicken Popcorn Recipe is a party appetizer which has succulent pieces of chicken with a crispy flavourful coating.

Name: Garlic Chicken Cheese Balls
Desc: Garlic Chicken Cheese Balls Recipe is minced chicken flavoured with garlic, stuffed with gooey mozzarella cheese deep fried to perfection.
